However, I extend my sincerest apologies to everyone present at the bar for the disturbance I caused. It is important to highlight that this incident is an anomaly in my otherwise law-abiding life.

Considering the circumstances surrounding this regrettable event, I humbly request leniency from the court. I am well aware of the impact of my actions and the consequences they entail. This experience has taught me invaluable lessons, and I am committed to my personal growth, making amends, and ensuring that such behavior never recurs in the future.

Thank you, Your Honor, for your kind attention.

